'''Nuagisme''' (literally "cloudism") is a French [[art-critical]] term that was advanced in the 1950s by art critic [[Julien Alvard]] (1916-1974).<ref>[http://bauddhamata.blogspot.de/2010/09/nuagisme.html Nuagisme, Clouds / sritantra, 2014]</ref>
